The cool thing about the remix 12" is that the A-side is double-grooved. So depending on which groove the needle hits, it will play either the Christmas Eve remix or the Christmas Day remix. I personally prefer the former remix because it really is like Psychocandy-era Mary Chain fronted by Bjork. The Christmas Day remix is similar but with a focus more on the drums and less on the feed backing guitars.

